verses.text_plain: O sing unto the Lord a new song; for he hath done marvellous things: his right hand, and his holy arm, hath gotten him the victory.
verses.verse_html: 1O sing unto the Lord a new song; for he hath done marvellous things: his right hand, and his holy arm, hath gotten him the victory.

verses.text_plain: The Lord hath made known his salvation: his righteousness hath he openly shewed in the sight of the heathen.
verses.verse_html:
2The Lord hath made known his salvation: his righteousness hath he openly shewed in the sight of the heathen. ▼
▼ openly…: or, revealed

verses.text_plain: He hath remembered his mercy and his truth toward the house of Israel: all the ends of the earth have seen the salvation of our God.
verses.verse_html: 3He hath remembered his mercy and his truth toward the house of Israel: all the ends of the earth have seen the salvation of our God.

verses.text_plain: Make a joyful noise unto the Lord, all the earth: make a loud noise, and rejoice, and sing praise.
verses.verse_html: 4Make a joyful noise unto the Lord, all the earth: make a loud noise, and rejoice, and sing praise.

verses.text_plain: Sing unto the Lord with the harp; with the harp, and the voice of a psalm.
verses.verse_html: 5Sing unto the Lord with the harp; with the harp, and the voice of a psalm.

verses.text_plain: With trumpets and sound of cornet make a joyful noise before the Lord, the King.
verses.verse_html: 6With trumpets and sound of cornet make a joyful noise before the Lord, the King.

verses.text_plain: Let the sea roar, and the fulness thereof; the world, and they that dwell therein.
verses.verse_html:
7Let the sea roar, and the fulness thereof; the world, and they that dwell therein. ▼
▼ the fulness…: or, all it containeth

footnotes.body_text: ▼ the fulness…: or, all it containeth
footnotes.body_html: ▼ the fulness…: or, all it containeth

verses.text_plain: Let the floods clap their hands: let the hills be joyful together
verses.verse_html: 8Let the floods clap their hands: let the hills be joyful together

verses.text_plain: Before the Lord; for he cometh to judge the earth: with righteousness shall he judge the world, and the people with equity.
verses.verse_html: 9Before the Lord; for he cometh to judge the earth: with righteousness shall he judge the world, and the people with equity.
